headline: Freeport CEO Says Tariffs Threaten to Hinder US Copper Mining
summary: (Bloomberg) -- The threat of US levies on copper imports has been a boon for Freeport-McMoRan Inc., with North America’s top producer cashing in on selling the metal at a premium.
